org.phantomapi.clust

Interface MultiDataHandler<T,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the Configurable object
    V - the bound object used to get the data
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataController, PlayerDataHandler, PlayerDataManager

    public interface MultiDataHandler<T,V>
    An interface for handing multiple data clustered objects with the same relative type. A Great example would be using this for playerdata
    Author:
    cyberpwn
